Remove the ParentalControls portal (age bracket querying API).

This portal allows applications to query the user's age bracket
via D-Bus. It was added in response to age verification laws
(CA AB-1043, CO SB26-051, Brazil Lei 15.211).

This patch removes the portal, its backend interface, the D-Bus
XML definitions, the implementation, and the test infrastructure.
It does not touch any other portal functionality.

Based on xdg-desktop-portal PR #1922.

